msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Important:</emphasis> The class-instance name must "
"be the same as the name of the event that triggers the task to be invoked. "
"CloudForms matches the class instance with the event by this name. To find "
"the event name, see <link xlink:href=\"http://sysmgt.lenovofiles.com/help/"
"topic/com.lenovo.lxca.doc/messages.html?cp=1_22_16\">Messages</link> in the "
"Lenovo XClarity Administrator online documentation."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">重要：</emphasis> 类实例名称必须与触发要调用的任务的事件名称相同。CloudForms "
"按照该名称来匹配类实例和事件。若要查找事件名称，请参见 Lenovo XClarity Administrator 在线文档中的<link xlink:"
"href=\"http://sysmgt.lenovofiles.com/help/topic/com.lenovo.lxca.doc/messages."
"html?cp=1_22_16\">消息</link>。"

msgid ""
"Add the path to the event handlers copied in the field’s <emphasis role="
"\"strong\">rel3</emphasis>."
msgstr "添加在字段的 <emphasis role=\"strong\">rel3</emphasis> 中复制的事件处理程序的路径。"

msgid "There are three available policy operations:"
msgstr "可用的策略操作有三种："

msgid "Physical Server Reset"
msgstr "物理服务器重置"

msgid "Physical Server Start"
msgstr "物理服务器启动"

msgid "Physical Server Shutdown"
msgstr "物理服务器关机"

msgid "There are three available policy events:"
msgstr "可用的策略事件有三种："

msgid "physical_server_reset"
msgstr "physical_server_reset"

msgid "physical_server_start"
msgstr "physical_server_start"

msgid "physical_server_shutdown"
msgstr "physical_server_shutdown"

msgid ""
"The policy actions and the policy events must match. For example, use the "
"following path to the policy operation <emphasis role=\"strong\">Physical "
"Server Shutdown</emphasis>:"
msgstr ""
"策略操作和策略事件必须匹配。例如，使用策略操作<emphasis role=\"strong\">物理服务器关机</emphasis>的以下路径："

msgid ""
"/System/event_handlers/event_action_policy? target="
"physical_server&amp;policy_event=physical_server_shutdown&amp;param=\n"
"The policy_event value is matched with the policy operation applied."
msgstr ""
"/System/event_handlers/event_action_policy? target="
"physical_server&amp;policy_event=physical_server_shutdown&amp;param=\n"
"policy_event 值与应用的策略操作匹配。"

msgid "Step 3. Create a namespace."
msgstr "第 3 步：创建命名空间。"

msgid "Select the custom domain (<emphasis role=\"strong\">Lenovo</emphasis>) ."
msgstr "选择自定义域 (<emphasis role=\"strong\">Lenovo</emphasis>)。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration &gt; Add a New Namespace</"
"emphasis> from the top menu."
msgstr "单击顶部菜单中的<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置 &gt; 添加新的命名空间</emphasis>。"

msgid "Enter a unique name for the namespace (for example, Functions)."
msgstr "输入命名空间的唯一名称（例如，Functions）。"

msgid "Step 4. Create a class."
msgstr "第 4 步：创建类。"

msgid ""
"Select the namespace that you created in the previous step (for example, "
"Functions)."
msgstr "选择您在上一步中创建的命名空间（例如，Functions）。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration &gt; Add a New Class</"
"emphasis> from the top menu."
msgstr "单击顶部菜单中的<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置 &gt; 添加新的类</emphasis>。"

msgid "Enter a unique name for the class (for example, Power_actions)."
msgstr "输入类的唯一名称（例如，Power_actions）。"

msgid "Step 5. Create a method for the class."
msgstr "第 5 步：创建类的方法。"

msgid "Create a method."
msgstr "创建方法。"

msgid "Select the class that you created (for example, Power_actions)."
msgstr "选您创建的类（例如 Power_actions）。"

msgid "Click the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Methods</emphasis> tab."
msgstr "单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">方法</emphasis>选项卡。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration &gt; Add a new method</"
"emphasis> from the top menu."
msgstr "单击顶部菜单中的<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置 &gt; 添加新的方法</emphasis>。"

msgid "Select <emphasis role=\"strong\">“inline”</emphasis> for the type."
msgstr "选择 <emphasis role=\"strong\">“inline”</emphasis> 作为类型。"

msgid "Enter a name for the method (for example, power_off)."
msgstr "输入方法的名称（例如，power_off）。"

msgid ""
"Enter the following script in the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Data</emphasis> "
"field:"
msgstr "在<emphasis role=\"strong\">数据</emphasis>字段中输入以下脚本："

msgid ""
"server = $evm.vmdb('PhysicalServer').first $evm.log(:info, \"Powering Server "
"#{server.name} OFF\")\n"
"server.power_off exit MIQ_OK"
msgstr ""
"server = $evm.vmdb('PhysicalServer').first $evm.log(:info, \"Powering Server "
"#{server.name} OFF\")\n"
"server.power_off exit MIQ_OK"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Validate</emphasis> to verify the syntax."
msgstr "单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">验证</emphasis>以验证语法。"

msgid "Add a schema to the class."
msgstr "为类添加一个模式。"

msgid "Select the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Schema</emphasis> tab."
msgstr "选择<emphasis role=\"strong\">模式</emphasis>选项卡。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration &gt; Edit selected Schema</"
"emphasis> from the top menu."
msgstr "单击顶部菜单中的<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置 &gt; 编辑所选模式</emphasis>。"

msgid ""
"Click the <emphasis role=\"strong\">+</emphasis> icon to add a field to the "
"schema."
msgstr "单击 <emphasis role=\"strong\">+</emphasis> 图标，为该模式添加一个字段。"

msgid "Enter <emphasis role=\"strong\">“execute”</emphasis> for the name."
msgstr "输入 <emphasis role=\"strong\">“execute”</emphasis> 作为名称。"

msgid "Select <emphasis role=\"strong\">“Method”</emphasis> for the type"
msgstr "选择 <emphasis role=\"strong\">“Method”</emphasis> 作为类型"

msgid "Select <emphasis role=\"strong\">“String”</emphasis> for the data type."
msgstr "选择 <emphasis role=\"strong\">“String”</emphasis> 作为数据类型。"

msgid ""
"Enter <emphasis role=\"strong\">“Power_actions”</emphasis> for the default "
"value."
msgstr "输入 <emphasis role=\"strong\">“Power_actions”</emphasis> 作为默认值。"

msgid "Click the check mark icon."
msgstr "单击勾号图标。"

msgid "Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Save</emphasis>."
msgstr "单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">保存</emphasis>。"

msgid "Add the method to the class."
msgstr "添加方法到该类。"

msgid "Select the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Instances</emphasis> tab."
msgstr "选择<emphasis role=\"strong\">实例</emphasis>选项卡。"

msgid ""
"Enter the name of the method that you created earlier (for example, "
"power_off)."
msgstr "输入您之前创建的方法的名称（例如， power_off）。"

msgid "Invoking an automated task when an event occurs"
msgstr "在事件发生时调用自动化任务"

msgid ""
"To automatically invoke the task when a certain event occurs, you must "
"create, configure and assign a custom policy."
msgstr "若要在特定事件发生时自动调用任务，您必须创建、配置和分配自定义策略。"

msgid ""
"As an example, the following steps describe how to perform a specific "
"automated task when CloudForms receives certain events (that you define)."
msgstr "例如，下列步骤描述了如何在 CloudForms 收到（您定义的）特定事件时执行一个特定的自动化任务。"

msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Note:</emphasis> You must be logged in to "
"CloudForms as a user with permission to create policies. The default user is "
"admin, password smartvm."
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">注意：</emphasis> 您必须以有权创建策略的用户身份登录 CloudForms。默认用户为 "
"admin，密码为 smartvm。"

msgid "Step 1. Create and configure a policy."
msgstr "第 1 步：创建和配置策略。"

msgid "Navigate to <emphasis role=\"strong\">Control &gt; Explorer</emphasis>."
msgstr "前往<emphasis role=\"strong\">控制 &gt; 浏览器</emphasis>。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Policies &gt; All Policies &gt; Control "
"Policies &gt; Physical Infrastructure Control Policies</emphasis>."
msgstr ""
"单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">策略 &gt; 所有策略 &gt; 控制策略 &gt; 物理基础架构控制策略</"
"emphasis>。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration &gt; Add a new Physical Server "
"Control Policy</emphasis> from the top menu."
msgstr "单击顶部菜单中的<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置 &gt; 添加新的物理服务器控制策略</emphasis>。"

msgid "Enter a description (for example, Lenovo_Policy)."
msgstr "输入描述（例如，Lenovo_Policy）。"

msgid "Step 2. Create a custom action."
msgstr "第 2 步：创建自定义操作。"

msgid "Create a custom action."
msgstr "创建自定义操作。"

msgid ""
"Navigation to <emphasis role=\"strong\">Action &gt; All Actions</emphasis>."
msgstr "前往<emphasis role=\"strong\">动作 &gt; 所有动作</emphasis>。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration &gt; Add a new action</"
"emphasis> from the top menu."
msgstr "单击顶部菜单中的<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置 &gt; 添加新的动作</emphasis>。"

msgid "Enter a description (for example, Power_Off_Server)."
msgstr "输入描述（例如，Power_Off_Server）。"

msgid ""
"For Action Type select <emphasis role=\"strong\">Invoke a custom Automation</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr "选择<emphasis role=\"strong\">调用自定义自动化</emphasis>作为操作类型。"

msgid "Enter a message (for example, create)."
msgstr "输入相关的消息（例如，create）。"

msgid ""
"Fill the Request field with <emphasis role=\"strong\">Call_Instance</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr "在“请求”字段中填入 <emphasis role=\"strong\">Call_Instance</emphasis>。"

msgid "Specify the following attributes in the order give:"
msgstr "按照所给的顺序指定下列属性："

msgid ""
"Specify the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Namespace</emphasis> attribute, and "
"set the value to the new domain and namespace (&lt;domain_name&gt;/"
"&lt;namespace&gt;) (for example, Lenovo/Functions)."
msgstr ""
"指定<emphasis role=\"strong\">命名空间</emphasis>属性，并将其值设为新的域和命名空间 "
"(&lt;domain_name&gt;/&lt;namespace&gt;)（例如，Lenovo/Functions）。"

msgid ""
"Specify the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Class</emphasis> attribute, and set "
"the value to the class (for example, Power_actions)."
msgstr ""
"指定<emphasis role=\"strong\">类</emphasis> 属性，并将其值设为对应的类（例如，Power_actions）。"

msgid ""
"Specify the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Instance</emphasis> attribute, and set "
"the value to the instance (for example, Physical_Server_PowerOff)."
msgstr ""
"指定<emphasis role=\"strong\">实例</"
"emphasis>属性，并将其值设为对应的实例（例如，Physical_Server_PowerOff）。"

msgid "Configure the policy that you created."
msgstr "配置您创建的策略。"

msgid "Select the new policy (for example, Lenovo_Policy)."
msgstr "选择新策略（例如，Lenovo_Policy）。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration &gt; Edit this policy’s Event "
"assignments</emphasis> from the top menu."
msgstr "单击顶部菜单中的<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置 &gt; 编辑这个策略的事件分配</emphasis>。"

msgid ""
"Find Physical Server operation, and select the <emphasis role="
"\"strong\">Physical Server Shutdown</emphasis> option."
msgstr "找到物理服务器操作，再选择<emphasis role=\"strong\">物理服务器关机</emphasis>选项。"

msgid "Select the new policy event."
msgstr "选择新策略事件。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration &gt; Edit Actions for this "
"policy Event</emphasis> from the top menu."
msgstr "单击顶部菜单中的<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置 &gt; 为这个策略事件编辑动作</emphasis>。"

msgid ""
"From the <emphasis role=\"strong\">Order of Actions if All Conditions are "
"True</emphasis> field, select the custom action that you created in the "
"previous step (for example, Power_Off_Server)."
msgstr ""
"从<emphasis role=\"strong\">如果所有条件都为 True 时的动作顺序</emphasis> "
"字段中，选择您在上一步中创建的自定义操作（例如，Power_Off_Server）。"

msgid "Step 3. Create and assign a policy profile."
msgstr "第 3 步：创建和分配策略配置集。"

msgid "Create a policy profile."
msgstr "创建策略配置集。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Policy Profiles &gt; All Policy Profiles</"
"emphasis>."
msgstr "单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">策略配置集 &gt; 所有策略配置集</emphasis>。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Configuration &gt; Add a new Policy Profile</"
"emphasis> from the top menu."
msgstr "单击顶部菜单中的<emphasis role=\"strong\">配置 &gt; 添加新的策略配置集</emphasis>。"

msgid ""
"Enter a description for the policy (for example, Lenovo_Policy_Profile)."
msgstr "输入策略的描述（例如，Lenovo_Policy_Profile）。"

msgid "Select your policy and drag it to the right."
msgstr "选择您的策略，并将它拖到右侧。"

msgid ""
"Assign the policy profile to the Lenovo physical-infrastructure providers:"
msgstr "将策略配置集分配到 Lenovo 物理基础架构供应商："

msgid ""
"Select the physical-infrastructure providers to which you want to assign the "
"policy profile."
msgstr "指定您要向其分配策略配置集的物理基础架构供应商。"

msgid ""
"Click <emphasis role=\"strong\">Policy &gt; Manage Policies</emphasis> form "
"the top menu."
msgstr "从顶部菜单中，单击<emphasis role=\"strong\">策略 &gt; 管理策略</emphasis>。"

msgid ""
"Select the policy profile that you just created (for example, "
"Lenovo_Policy_Profile)."
msgstr "选择您刚刚创建的策略配置集（例如，Lenovo_Policy_Profile）。"

